		<li class="NavIcon"><a href="./Profile" class="NavButtLink"><img class="NavButt" src="/WeConnectPlus-Front/assets/Logo-Black.png"/></a></li>
		<li class="NavIcon"><a href="./Connect" class="NavButtLink"><img class="NavButt" src="/WeConnectPlus-Front/assets/chat.svg"/></a></li>
